&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;np.flatten()&lt;/strong&gt; - copy&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;np.ravel()&lt;/strong&gt; - no copy, it means that any manipulation on it will be saved&lt;/p&gt;

